songs.title: Superstar
songs.lyrics:
Sanu sona lagda ve
Tera ni mitha hasna
Pai tu kameez kaali oe
Tenu sajda
Silky silky ni baal utton
Tera nachna
Dil kar da ve mera
Tenu main takla
Keh ke tun vekh zara
Main tera banjhawa
Dil tenu de davan
Honke tu meri
Superstar
Tenu kehda intazar
Main tera dildar
Tu meri superstar
Tenu hath lawa main
Bijjli da penda chatka
440 watt da, tera ek
Thumka
Tere te akh sekh sekh
Nai mein rajjda
Baby gal meri mun tu
Seenye lagja
Carmen electra di
Paenh menu tu lagni en
Sanu ve dede tu chen
Sanu tarsanie
Nachange
Nachange
Nachange saari raat
Lakhan je tuwi ek
Chamke ni like a star
Keh ke tun vekh zara
Main tera banjhawa
Dil tenu de davan

Honke tu meri
Superstar
Tenu kehda intazar
Main tera dildar
Tu meri superstar
Main tera banjhawa
Dil tenu de davan
Honke tu meri
Superstar
